  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and let them sizzle for 10 seconds.",
    "Add onion, ginger, and garlic. Cook until onion is translucent.",
    "Add tomato and cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Add sausages and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add cumin powder, coriander powder, red chili powder, garam masala, and salt. Mix well.",
    "Add water and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let it simmer for 15 minutes.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro and serve hot.",
    "Serve with rice or roti for a filling meal"
